value.string: This condominium residence offers the highest level of luxury living in the heart of Kaanapali, located on the world famous Kaanapali Beach. The past winner of the Maikai Loa Award given by the National Kitchen and Bath Association and the Whos Who Award in the Designer Kitchen Magazine, this home contains features such as: German SieMatic oak vertical grain cabinetry throughout the kitchen and bathroom flat panel framed door Matte Lacquer finish Sub-Zero refrigerator Amana 30-inch Black ceran cooktop and microwave with custom trim kit Best island hood Creda oven Miele integrated dishwasher Maytag disposal wood and Baltic Brown granite countertops with bullnose edge Franke stainless steel undermount sink with chrome air switch and controller KWC Domo chrome faucet Everpure chrome faucet Eurostone concrete tile flooring Hera under cabinet halogen lighting and low voltage recessed cans. This unit has been completely remodeled and is one of the few units with two and a half baths. Seller will consider any offers of Seller Financing dependent on terms and conditions.Newly Replaced: Refrigerator, Stove-top, oven, microwave, dishwasher & washer & dryer.

A rare beachfront offering on Maui's world famous Keawakapu Beach. This family estate offers over 5700 sq. ft. of interior space, and is situated on over half an acre which boasts a true tropical feeling with ample indoor/outdoor areas. Enjoy the private pool beachfront setting with cascading waterfalls, cabana/bar area, large Jacuzzi and spacious lawn.
